OL,4,CSA headteacher 'made pupil dig in poo
OL,5,Cfor lost phone'
OL,6, A South African headmaster has been
OL,7, suspended over accusations he forced an
OL,8, 11-year-old boy to dig for a missing
OL,9, phone in a faeces-filled pit latrine.
OL,11,FHe is alleged to have lowered the child
OL,12,Fby a rope into the hole used for a
OL,13,Ftoilet, promising him 200 rand ($14;
OL,14,F#10).
OL,16,FThe boy's grandmother says he now fears
OL,17,Fgoing to school as other pupils mocked
OL,18,Fhim afterwards.
OL,20,FThe local education body told TimesLive
OL,21,Fit learned of the matter with "shame".
